                    <div class="right">
                        <figure class="back"
                            style="background-image: url(http://artisticdesigning.com/Drawings/Photoshopped/intex_speakers.jpg);">
                            <div class="font">
                                <img src="img/advance.png" alt="" style="margin: -5vh 10vh 2vh 15vh;transform: scale(0.7);">

                                <p>退&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp水&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp在警長競選時上警並在投票前放棄競選</p>
                                <p>反&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp水&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp在接到起跳預言家的金水時不相信該玩家</p>
                                <p>奶&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp穿&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp同時因狼人擊殺、女巫解藥和守衛守護而死亡</p>
                                <p>綁&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp票&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp當場上狼人數>=好人數時，狼人放逐某玩家</p>
                                <p>貼&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp臉&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp情緒化發言使場上玩家強制認下自己好人身份</p>
                                <p>擦&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp邊&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp運用場外信息暗示自己是好人身份</p>
                                <p>鍊&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp子&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp被丘比特的技能選中，成為情侶的玩家</p>
                                <p>好&nbsp&nbsp人&nbsp&nbsp鏈&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp情侶雙方都是好人</p>
                                <p>狼&nbsp&nbsp狼&nbsp&nbsp鏈&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp情侶雙方都是狼人</p>
                                <p>人&nbsp&nbsp狼&nbsp&nbsp鏈&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp雙方一個是好人一個是壞人的情侶的情況</p>
                                <p>詐&nbsp&nbsp身&nbsp&nbsp份&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp在警上為了試探後置位玩家身份進行的操作</p>
                                <p>積&nbsp&nbsp身&nbsp&nbsp份&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp神民隱藏自己的身份</p>
                            </div>
                        </figure>
                        <figure class="front"
