                                <p>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp睡&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp攝夢人使用攝夢技能</p>
                                <p>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp連&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp丘比特選擇情侶</p>
                                <p>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp埋&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp被盜賊棄掉的另外一張身份底牌</p>
                                <p>盲&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp守&nbsp&nbsp|&nbsp&nbsp守衛在不知任何信息時選擇守護一名其他玩家</p>
